<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 5 (Cless) - End</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>クレス</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Cless</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>チェスター</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Chester</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>エターナルソードもリアラのもとに返したし
これで本当に終わったんだね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We've given the sword back to Reala,
so this really is the end now, huh.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……そうだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Guess it is.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>後悔……してるのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Do you... regret it?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なに言ってんだよ。
そんなの当たりめぇだろ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Heck are you asking?
Of course I do.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>だがよ、例え後悔しても
アミィの望んでない道を選ぶ事は出来ねぇ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But even if I regret it, I can't go down
a path that Ami wouldn't want for me.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>たとえエターナルソードが
聖剣のままだったとしても
アミィは使っちゃいけねぇと考えたはずだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Even if the Eternal Sword stayed a holy sword,
Ami wouldn't have thought it should be used.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Need to revisit this after having more context.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうだね。　過去は変えられない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah. We can't change the past.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>だからこそ、
今を必死で生きる事に意味があるんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's why living our lives
to the fullest has meaning.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>生きていこうぜ。
オレ達で力を合わせてよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's go live on.
Together, with everything we've got.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Unreferenced</Section>
